name: 奥利维亚·杜凯恩
name_full: 奥利维亚·杜凯恩 Olivia Ducayen
introduction: Olivia Ducayen is a Canadian Actor from Vancouver, BC. She is best known for Sorry About the Demon (2022) and B-Side (Short) which screened at Whistler Film Festival, (2019) Vancouver International Short Film Festival, (2020) and was Nominated for a Leo award for Best Short Drama. Olivia grew up doing community theatre on Bowen Island, and starred in her first short film at the age of 13. She graduated from Capilano University with a Diploma in Acting for Stage and Screen in 2019.
